description: Discover this unique 1-bedroom condo in a stunning converted church, steps from the Broadway Train Station. Boasting an open layout filled with natural light, this unit features a modern kitchen, in-unit laundry, central AC, and custom California closets. With 1 off-street parking space included, enjoy the blend of historic charm and contemporary living. The condo is ideal for those seeking a stylish, maintenance-free home in a prime location. The location is central to multiple restaurants, public transportation, and the vibrant neighborhoods of South Boston, South End, and the Seaport. Experience easy living with convenient amenities and a lifestyle surrounded by the city's nightlife and culinary delights.
